To create/update an image form a existing image:
1. boot a vm with latest image. #only one nic is supported#, default gw should be setup by dhcp
2. wait until it comes online, make sure the SG(security group) allows connections to remote desktop
3. set the password of user, force change on next login.
4. download and execute Cloudbase-Init, installer may be on c:\
5. select Run sysprep and shutdown. the vm will stop.
6. select username Admin
7. select Administrators group
8. select port COM1
9. take an snapshot of the vm
